<td data-valign="top"><p>EALA-BHI, eala-bhi,<br />
Mo niarach neach aig am bi,<br />
Buaineam thu le mo lamh dheas,<br />
Teasdam thu le mo lamh chli,<br />
Ga ba co a gheabh thu ’n cro an ail,<br />
Cha bhi e gu brath gun ni.</p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p> </p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>SAINT JOHN'S wort, Saint John's wort,<br />
My envy whosoever has thee,<br />
I will pluck thee with my right hand,<br />
I will preserve thee with my left hand,<br />
Whoso findeth thee in the cattle fold,<br />
Shall never be without kine.</p></td>
